                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">What if a fifteen minute recast were added to C3 (KEI)?  Something similar would have to be done to C4, C5, etc. at the same time.
<br />

<br />
It would have a huge effect in PoK, effectively reducing the supply.  That would in turn increase the demand for enchanters in groups.  It would also tend to reduce the sharing of enchanters among several groups in busy zones.
<br />

<br />
It would make more than one enchanter needed for a raid, especially after a wipe.  They might tend to be botted enchanters though.
<br />

<br />
What it would not affect is buffbots on second accounts who are parked out-of-group while the main character plays.
<br />

<br />
Would it be worth it?</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
