                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Sylphan wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">What if a fifteen minute recast were added to C3 (KEI)?  Something similar would have to be done to C4, C5, etc. at the same time.
